<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="ja">
<body class="bg-background text-on-background font-body-md selection:bg-primary-fixed selection:text-on-primary-fixed">

<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-20 pb-32 overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-gutter relative z-10">
<div class="max-w-3xl">
<h1 class="font-headline-lg text-[48px] leading-tight mb-6 text-on-surface">
                        参加できなかったイベントの<br/>
<span class="text-primary">「誰に聞けばいいか」</span>がわかる
                    </h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-xl">
                        イベントログを整理し、話題と関係者を可視化します。
                        膨大なDiscordのやり取りを追う必要はもうありません。
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">

  <%= link_to "無料で始める",
              new_user_registration_path,
              class: "px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-primary text-on-primary font-headline-md shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:scale-105 transition-all" %>

  <%= link_to "イベント一覧を見る",
              events_path,
              class: "px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant font-headline-md hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all" %>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Decorative Element (Simple SVG representation of visualization) -->
<div class="absolute right-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden lg:block w-1/2 h-[500px] opacity-20">
<div class="w-full h-full border-2 border-primary-fixed border-dashed rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse">
<div class="w-2/3 h-2/3 border-2 border-secondary-fixed border-dashed rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- 4 Step Guide -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-lowest" id="how-it-works">

<div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-gutter grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<!-- Step 1 -->
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">add_circle</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">1. イベント作成</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">開催されたイベントの基本情報を入力。</p>
<div class="step-line hidden md:block"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 2 -->
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">label</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">2. 話題登録</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">話された主なテーマ（トピック）を登録。</p>
<div class="step-line hidden md:block"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 3 -->
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">content_paste</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">3. ログ貼り付け</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Discordのチャットログをそのままペースト。</p>
<div class="step-line hidden md:block"></div>
</div>
<!-- Step 4 -->
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-primary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 z-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">visibility</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">4. 確認</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">自動で整理された話題と関係者を把握。</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Features (Bento Grid Style) -->
<section class="py-24 px-gutter max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">


  <p class="text-center text-on-surface-variant mb-16">
    最近投稿されたイベント
  </p>

  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">

    <% Event.order(created_at: :desc).limit(3).each do |event| %>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl p-card-padding border border-outline-variant shadow-sm">

        <h3 class="font-headline-md mb-2">
          <%= event.title %>
        </h3>

        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-4">
          投稿者: <%= event.user.name %>
        </p>

        <%= link_to "詳細を見る",
                    event_path(event),
                    class: "text-primary" %>

      </div>

    <% end %>

  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-12">
    <%= link_to "イベント一覧を見る",
                events_path,
                class: "px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-primary text-on-primary" %>
  </div>



</section>
</main>

<script>
        // Micro-interactions and simple effects
        

        // Sticky header transparency effect
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const header = document.querySelector('header');
            if (window.scrollY > 20) {
                header.classList.add('bg-surface/90', 'backdrop-blur-md');
            } else {
                header.classList.remove('bg-surface/90', 'backdrop-blur-md');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body></html>